# CLIP ChangeLog for www-servers/nginx

  25 Jan 2016; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  nginx-1.7.6-r1.ebuild:
  Fix clip-lib dependency.

*nginx-1.7.6-r1 (27 May 2015)

  27 May 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +nginx-1.7.6-r1.ebuild, -nginx-1.7.6.ebuild, files/clip/rb/nginx.conf,
  +files/clip/rb/jail/netfilter:
  Set listen port to 2600 and disable NET_BIND_SERVICE for clip-rb.
  Add Netfilter rules for incoming TCP connections on the black or red sides.

*nginx-1.7.8 (15 Apr 2015)

  15 Apr 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +nginx-1.7.8.ebuild, +files/nginx-1.7.6-clip-chroot.patch,
  +files/nginx-1.7.6-clip-log.patch, +files/clip/rb*:
  Initial CLIP import for clip-rb:
  * add two new jails (rb_black:601 and rb_red:602) in /vservers
  * add chroot patch (still need access to /dev/log): chroot in /srv
  * add log patch: remove date from core logs
  * start Nginx in the jail and then chroot in a minimal /srv
  * import net addresses from /etc/conf.d/jail-net (RB_{BLACK,RED}{,_LOCAL}_ADDR)
  * create syslog configuration
  * add Nginx configuration
